{"tid":1656130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[1018人鏈無人講？] 不如試吓善用推文回覆，所有推文回覆用[1018 18區人鏈 1020民陣九龍大遊行]","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T17:06:47.000Z","uid":128994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85b7b0c6fbcb2f8319dc311fd23c1553e0535f3d","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩個post推吾郁，所以再post多次，想查案嘅唔緊要， <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但不如試吓所有推文既回應都用&rdquo; 1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>，所有post都用呢個回應去推文，我地818之前都係咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個熱門得一個行動post，好掛住以前一開熱門就七八個行動post，查案梗要，但係出嚟行動都非常重要。<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018究竟係咪搞，除左824之外，無一次係搞得成功，今次完全無人提過details同宣傳過！</span></span> 人鏈真係要時間宣傳，先做到效果，吾好覺得和理非活動就忽略咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣唔搞大遊行，又話人哋唔搞，人哋申請，你地又唔宣傳，咁你哋咪繼續等去申請不反對通知書先宣傳，睇吓等到幾時<br />\n<br />\n經過上兩個星期既失誤，檢討完，又話要一星期前加大文宣，貼連儂牆，連登開post文宣，宜家呢？係咪想永遠星期四五先開始文宣，然後星期日之後又要賽後檢討話，冇計啦宣傳得太急，下次做返好佢啦！<br />\n<br />\n似撚次都咁樣樣，仲有幾多個下次？<br />\n<br />\n想同大家講多次，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋已經失去左二千幾個手足，仲有唔知幾多條人命！我哋呢次輸，唔係輸十年，係輸一世呀！！！香港人真係冇得再輸！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非活動，定和勇活動缺一不可，都好重要，請善用推文回覆。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkrpZ6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkrpZ6o.jpg&h=041e45ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zOMJwc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOMJwc4.jpg&h=1dcc10ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2jnMMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2jnMMu.png&h=df5480b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddfe7fe0484565845ebf5cb68439a146417cc9c8","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>"},{"pid":"988faa46df58ec98eb734322cf311ceb208e23ba","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>"},{"pid":"218a1d4ccaf48554870809ac2e950937943afdad","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>"},{"pid":"ca0ed0007cb9a813e157c6a218616a16ef311668","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>"},{"pid":"f6425a28b7915468c67500c2b35c20b6780d3689","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:15:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>"},{"pid":"1296ed4cb01be847dfacb8230f6d3a2d7c0d14b8","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>"},{"pid":"af7060e010d576dc3c4a3826a5bac38c7adbaa88","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:17:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1018 18區人鏈 1020九龍民陣大遊行</span></span>"},{"pid":"a8b671aac9711c904e6c505a1f52e17ffa9e1996","tid":1656130,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span